      "content": "idk i feel like u are downplaying the gas side a bit. u keep calling it a \"transitional fuel\" and saying it's \"cleaner than coal,\" but isnt its whole purpose just to keep burning fossil fuels because it's easier for companies? if we focus on gas too much arent we just delaying the actual solutions?",
